data.description: Tastefully updated 4 bedroom ranch located in the quiet Riverside Subdivision. Many updates all within the last two years including brand new siding and gutters, windows throughout, luxury vinyl flooring as well as an egress window in the basement bedroom. Enjoy summer nights on the patio in your pet friendly fenced in back yard. Located adjacent to the Milan Nature Park and conveniently located a few blocks from the local grocery store. Come and see if this is the house that can be called home.
